getFirstMinimalConversionsFrom

public GameType[] getFirstMinimalConversionsFrom(GameType src)
Returns the first minimal conversions from a game of a specified source type to an equivalent game of this type. If the conversion is possible, an array of types {t1, t2, ..., tn} will be returned such that t1 is the source automaton type, tn is this automaton type, and direct conversions from ti to ti+1 are supported.

Parameters:
src - the source game type
Returns:
the minimal conversions from a game of the specified source type to an equivalent game of this type, or an empty array is the conversion is not supported
